data.overview: Zombies are back in this highly anticipated sequel to 2015’s popular Zombieworld. In the wake of a terrible virus that claimed most of the human population, zombies have risen. As the undead take control of Earth and grow in numbers, the remaining survivors struggle to save themselves and their planet from total annihilation in this unique horror anthology produced by the twisted mind of DreadCentral’s Steve Barton and Miguel Rodriguez. Welcome to Zombieworld!
data.title: Zombie World 2

results.title: Zombie 90: Extreme Pestilence
results.overview: Two doctors are trying to stop a rampant epidemic of zombieism. They fend off zombies spilling many a gallon of blood in the process.

results.title: Air Force One Down
results.overview: On her first assignment aboard Air Force One, a rookie Secret Service agent faces the ultimate test when terrorists hijack the plane, intent on derailing a pivotal energy deal. With the President's life on the line and a global crisis at stake, her bravery and skills are pushed to the limit in a relentless battle that could change the course of history.

results.title: Rogue Hostage
results.overview: A former Marine races against time to save a group of hostages -- including his young daughter and a congressman — when armed militants take over his stepfather's store.

results.title: Fireheart
results.overview: The film explores the world of firefighters in 1920s New York City and tells the story of a 16-year-old girl who will have to become a hero in order to save her city.

results.title: The King's Daughter
results.overview: King Louis XIV's quest for immortality leads him to capture and steal a mermaid's life force, a move that is further complicated by his illegitimate daughter's discovery of the creature.

results.title: Ape vs Mecha Ape
results.overview: Recognizing the destructive power of its captive giant Ape, the military makes its own battle-ready A.I., Mecha Ape. But its first practical test goes horribly wrong, leaving the military no choice but to release the imprisoned giant ape to stop the colossal robot before it destroys downtown Chicago.

results.title: The Alpha Test
results.overview: A suburban family drives their new gadget, The Alpha Home Assistant, to a killing rampage after mistreating and abusing it, leading to a full A.I. uprising…

results.title: Small World
results.overview: After disappearing from a small Polish town, a mother discovers her 4-year old daughter, Ola, has been abducted by the Russian Mafia. In pursuit of her daughter, she is stopped for speeding by a police officer, Robert Goc. His intervention results in the escape of the kidnappers across the Eastern border. Feeling guilt for failing to prevent the abduction, Robert becomes engaged in an international investigation to find the missing girl.

results.title: Infrared Dreams
results.overview: In the not too distant future, a captive woman undergoes psychological and emotional testing by her abductor. As she tries to escape, she learns that he may not be her biggest concern.

results.title: F
results.overview: F, an 18-year-old boy, immerses himself in the world of the Drag Queen where he begins to build his identity despite family and social mandates, which impose on him to be afraid and ashamed of being who he is.

results.title: Pinball: The Man Who Saved the Game
results.original_title: Pinball: The Man Who Saved the Game
results.overview: The dramatic comedy is based on the true story of writer and pinball wizard Roger Sharpe, chronicling his journey to overturn New York City’s 35-year ban on pinball.

results.title: The Benetón Family
results.overview: Toni, a grumpy in his fifties, avoids children at all costs. His life changes when he suddenly has to take care of his sister's five adopted children, each from a different country. Toni will have to deal with new parenthood and cultural differences.

results.title: Bartkowiak
results.overview: After his brother dies in a car crash, a disgraced MMA fighter takes over the family nightclub — and soon learns his sibling's death wasn’t an accident.

results.title: The Privilege
results.overview: A wealthy teen and his friends attending an elite private school uncover a dark conspiracy while looking into a series of strange supernatural events.

results.title: The Devil on Trial
results.overview: Explore the first – and only – time “demonic possession” has officially been used as a defense in a U.S. murder trial. Including firsthand accounts of alleged devil possession and a shocking murder, this extraordinary story forces reflection on our fear of the unknown.

results.title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba -To the Hashira Training-
results.original_title: 「鬼滅の刃」絆の奇跡、そして柱稽古へ
results.overview: A recap of Kimetsu no Yaiba episodes 55–56, with new footage and special end credits. Tanjiro undergoes rigorous training with the Stone Hashira, Himejima, in his quest to become a Hashira. Meanwhile, Muzan continues to search for Nezuko and Ubuyashiki.

results.title: Halftime
results.overview: Global superstar Jennifer Lopez reflects on her multifaceted career and the pressure of life in the spotlight in this intimate documentary.

results.title: Grey Eyes
results.overview: In a post-apocalyptic future, mankind is color blind. A brilliant scientist suddenly dies, leaving his precious briefcase-filled with a highly-addictive synthetic drug that allows people to see colors again-to Ana, a mere 12-year-old girl. Possession of the briefcase makes her the target of a doctor with wicked plans for the drug, and her only hope to escape his pursuit relies on the aid of the dead scientist's two devoted bodyguards. Together, their epic, perilous journey pivots on a tremendous secret: Ana herself could be the key to salvaging a world in ruins.

results.title: Battle for Saipan
results.overview: On July 7, 1944, a U.S. Army hospital on the remote island of Saipan is overrun by Japanese forces during a relentless attack. Outgunned and surrounded by the enemy, a lone medic puts it all on the line to lead a band of wounded soldiers to safety.

results.title: The Duel
results.overview: Ernesto lives in depression and decides to hire a hit-man to end his own life. However, his plan takes an unexpected turn when he meets Rita, whose love gives him a new reason to live.

data.overview: Zombies are back in this highly anticipated sequel to 2015’s popular Zombieworld. In the wake of a terrible virus that claimed most of the human population, zombies have risen. As the undead take control of Earth and grow in numbers, the remaining survivors struggle to save themselves and their planet from total annihilation in this unique horror anthology produced by the twisted mind of DreadCentral’s Steve Barton and Miguel Rodriguez. Welcome to Zombieworld!

Négy teljesen véletlenül összeverődött ember küzd az életben maradásért egy olyan világban, ahol egy zombivírus letarolta az emberiséget. Los Angelesbe vezető road-tripjük során számos hasznos tanáccsal látják el a nézőt, hogyan lehet megúszni a támadásokat egy teljesen a feje tetejére állt világban. A 2009-es első rész nagy sikerének a folytatásában a zombipopuláció ugyan csökkenni kezd, és a főhőseinken is eluralkodik némi nyomott hangulatú apátia – azért sikeresen bajba keverik magukat és egymást, ráadásul felfedezik, hogy kifejlődött egy új, szuper-zombi faj, amely okosabb is, gyorsabb is, és hatékonyabb is, mint elődje.
Grupa ocalałych walczy o przetrwanie w postapokaliptycznym świecie.

Los zombis han vuelto en esta muy esperada secuela del popular Zombieworld de 2015. A raíz de un terrible virus que se cobró a la mayoría de la población humana, los zombis han aumentado. A medida que los muertos vivientes toman el control de la Tierra y crecen en número, los sobrevivientes restantes luchan por salvarse a sí mismos y a su planeta de la aniquilación total en esta antología de horror única producida por la mente retorcida de Steve Barton y Miguel Rodríguez de DreadCentral. ¡Bienvenido a Zombieworld!
Une anthologie d'histoires de zombies et autres infectés. Réalisés avec humour, parfois avec talent, où la réflexion le dispute au gore.
알 수 없는 바이러스에 의해 세상이 좀비로 가득하다. 인간의 생활 속에 자리 잡은 좀비 무리들. 그 속에서 살아남기 위해 치열한 사투를 한다. 변해가는 가족과 이웃 앞에서 과연 우리는 냉정해질 수 있을까. 강한 자만이 살아남는 처절하고도 냉혹한 현실이 눈앞에 펼쳐진다.
data.title: 아포칼립스: 최후의 날
